    <title>Rework to Sheriff&#39;s Scout</title>
    <link>https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/rework-to-sheriffs-scout/57746</link>
    <description>Scout (day) - Target a player other than yourself and the king. You&#39;ll be alerted if a member of the unseen visit your target tonight. Mastermind visits aren&#39;t noticed until night 4. (Infinite)

Reasoning: I&#39;ve found scout to be a rather boring ability. Not only is it so hot and cold with what it does, it&#39;s also on sheriff. I&#39;ve had plenty of games where MM only gets a single convert off all game, and scout is rendered useless. 

With the new scout, it makes sharing logs more important and gives scout a real use other than auto detect that someone is converted. It also doesn&#39;t function as an auto &quot;oh you&#39;re converted&quot; strat since mm doesn&#39;t show up visiting until n4. By then he should have a full roster and his checks can be miss interpreted as converts.

My only real concern is this might give scout too much utility, as if mm keeps his logs with correct visits, he&#39;ll get found out by the scout.</description>
    
